\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35030,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/24\/sahl-on-futuwwah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38665,"position":3},"title":"Sahl on Presence: Believers relieved by living the present moment","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 24, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Sulami reported: It was asked of Sahl ibn Abdullah, may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cWhen will the soul of the impoverished find rest?\u201d Sahl said, \u201cWhen the soul does not see a moment other than the present moment in which it is.\u201d Al-Sulami said, \u201cIt is part of virtue\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34640,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/05\/masjid-home-every-taqi\/","url_meta":{"origin":38665,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Masajid: Mosques are the home of every righteous person","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 5, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe mosque is the home of every righteous person. Allah Almighty has guaranteed those who have their home in the mosques with the spirit, mercy, and safe passage over the bridge of Hell unto the pleasure\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\